To get started:

1) Copy settings.py.example to settings.py
2) Edit settings.py to add your MiraiEx Client ID and Secret Key and change bot parameters
3) Run it: python3 opusbot.py

Opus uses Requests which is an elegant and simple HTTP library for Python to interface with MiraiEx:
https://requests.readthedocs.io/en/master/

Support the maintainer of this robot by registering yourself at MiraiEX by visiting https://www.biltmore.no/miraiex/ or donate BTC to : 3DsMZSbD286Fj1rQThPBjPXxk4dkQtVHGe
